<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/logic-s-a" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6098093); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6098093&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610222217" alt="Logic S A" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6098093)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/logic-s-a" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6098093); return false;">Logic S A</a></span></p>
